@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF4FB
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #2E86AB
skinparam SequenceArrowColor #2E86AB
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #E8F8F5
skinparam NoteBorderColor #1ABC9C
skinparam SequenceDividerBackgroundColor #D5E8D4
skinparam SequenceDividerBorderColor #82B366

title **Phase 3 · Séquence (2/2) — Comparaison → Sauvegarde → Registre**

actor "Dev" as DEV

box "Python Process" #EBF4FB
  participant "Phase3\nPipeline" as P3
end box

box "Filesystem" #F0FFF4
  participant "models/" as FM
end box

box "Services" #FFF8E8
  participant "PostgreSQL\n:5432" as PG
  participant "MLflow\n:5001" as MLF
end box

== STEP 5 · Comparaison & Sélection Champion ==
P3  -> P3  : Tableau trié par F2-Score eval :
note right of P3
  Rang | Modèle           | F2    | AUC   | Recall | Overfit
  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  🏆   | lightgbm         | 0.621 | 0.823 | 0.714  | 0.012
       | xgboost          | 0.608 | 0.810 | 0.701  | 0.018
       | random_forest    | 0.571 | 0.789 | 0.668  | 0.025
       | gradient_boost   | 0.548 | 0.771 | 0.645  | 0.031
       | mlp+smote        | 0.522 | 0.752 | 0.621  | 0.029
       | logistic         | 0.498 | 0.731 | 0.603  | 0.008
       | decision_tree    | 0.441 | 0.699 | 0.571  | 0.041
       | dummy_baseline   | 0.089 | 0.501 | 0.104  | 0.000
end note

P3  -> MLF : set_tag(run_id_lgbm, "best_model", "true")\nset_tag(run_id_lgbm, "phase", "phase3_champion")

== STEP 6 · Sauvegarde Joblib + JSON ==
P3  -> FM  : joblib.dump(lgbm_model)\n→ **lightgbm_model.joblib**
P3  -> FM  : json.dump(metadata)\n→ **lightgbm_metadata.json**
note over FM
  {
    model_name: "lightgbm"
    model_class: "LGBMClassifier"
    is_best: true
    train_metrics: {f1:0.633, f2:0.633, auc:0.835}
    eval_metrics:  {f1:0.608, f2:0.621, auc:0.823}
    cv_f1_mean: 0.605  cv_f1_std: 0.011
    cv_auc_mean: 0.819 cv_auc_std: 0.008
    feature_names: [300 noms de colonnes]
    n_features: 300
    train_samples: 192428
    eval_samples:  48107
    target_rate: 0.0807
    mlflow_run_id: "abc123..."
    model_path: ".../lightgbm_model.joblib"
    saved_at: "2026-02-24T..."
  }
end note

== STEP 7 · Seuil Optimal ==
P3  -> P3  : y_proba = results["predictions"]["y_test_proba"]
P3  -> P3  : linspace(0.05, 0.80, 100)\nPour t : fbeta_score(y_eval, pred>=t, beta=2)
P3  -> P3  : optimal_threshold = t_max_f2\n→ ex. 0.35
note right of P3 : Seuil 0.5 inadapté
classes déséquilibrées
Phase 4 affinera avec COUT métier

== STEP 8 · Registre PostgreSQL ==
P3  -> PG  : INSERT INTO model_versions (\n  model_name = "lightgbm"\n  version    = "v_20260224_143201"\n  mlflow_run_id = "abc123..."\n  algorithm  = "LGBMClassifier"\n  hyperparameters = {n_estimators:200...} JSONB\n  metrics = {f2:0.621, auc:0.823...} JSONB\n  model_path = ".../lightgbm_model.joblib"\n  status = "trained"\n)
PG --> P3  : INSERT OK ✅

== Résumé Artefacts ==
note over FM
  **models/**
  lightgbm_model.joblib         ← champion
  lightgbm_metadata.json        ← is_best=true
  lightgbm_confusion_matrix.txt
  lightgbm_feature_importance.csv
  (+ fichiers des 7 autres modèles si --save-all)
end note

note over MLF
  **MLflow Expérience : Smart_Credit_Scoring**
  8 runs (1 par modèle) avec :
  Tags    : model_name, best_model, phase3
  Params  : model_*, cv_folds, n_features...
  Metrics : train/eval/cv F1, F2, AUC
            overfitting_f2, train_time_s
  Files   : model/ (sklearn), confusion .txt
            feature_importance .csv
end note

note over PG
  **PostgreSQL.model_versions**
  1 ligne insérée :
  version = "v_20260224_143201"
  status  = "trained"
  algorithm = "LGBMClassifier"
  optimal_threshold = NULL
  (sera mis à jour en Phase 4)
end note

DEV <-- P3 : pipeline {\n  .results (8 modèles)\n  .best_model_name = "lightgbm"\n  .mlflow_runs\n  .saved_model_paths\n}

note over DEV
  ⮕  Phase 4 :
  python -m src.pipelines.phase4_hyperparameter_tuning
  Lit lightgbm_metadata.json (is_best=True)
  Optimise les hyperparamètres du champion
end note

